HEADWORD: Quite
<hw>Quite</hw> <pr>(kw⟦imac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>See
<er>Quit</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
